ix86-Linux 2.1.x (libc5 and glibc2)
ix86-Linux 2.2.x (libc5 and glibc2)
ix86-Linux 2.3.x (glibc2.1)
ix86-Linux 2.4.x (glibc2.2)
ix86-FreeBSD 4.0-current
